426
00:34:56,609 --> 00:35:01,090
Good idea.
Well, uh, sorry for the inconvenience.

427
00:35:06,813 --> 00:35:14,296
You folks have a nice trip.
You, too.

428
00:35:17,857 --> 00:35:21,778
It's me, Caulfield.

429
00:35:22,379 --> 00:35:23,899
How you doing?
